== Afa Hyɛ ==
Wɔde nnuane ne nsa gye ahohoɔ wɔ afahyɛ no ase. Amanfoɔ no hyɛ wɔn amammerɛ ntadeɛ ahorɔw de kɔ dwa dataa a ahenfo no abɔ no ase. Asa ne nnwomtoɔ nso kɔ so wɔ afahyɛ no ase<ref>http://www.ghanaembassyiran.com/en/page/majorfestivals</ref>.

== Mfasoɔ ==
Wodi afahyɛ yi de kae nkunim a wɔn manfoɔ no dii wɔ nkoasom akofo so wɔn a wodi wɔn anim ne Babatu ne Samori wɔ afe 1896 mu<ref>https://www.ghanaweb.com/GhanaHomePage/NewsArchive/Government-to-spend-on-tourist-attractions-14577</ref>. Wɔsan nso nam afahyɛ no so srɛ wɔn anyame apɔwmuden ne nkwa tenten.<ref>http://www.s158663955.websitehome.co.uk/ghanaculture/mod_print.php?sectionid=530</ref>

